dct_title_s: Map of parts of the Districts of Nipissing and Algoma exhibiting the country around Sudbury and eastward to the Ottawa River
dct_alternative_sm: Map of parts of the districts of Nipissing and Algoma : exhibiting the country around Sudbury and eastward to the Ottawa River / complied form plans of a survey by the Department of Crown Lands, Toronto, and plans of survey by the Geological Survey Department, Ottawa.
dct_description_sm: Colors indicate the geological composition. Map also shows townships, rivers, lakes, railroad lines, Indian reserves, and other points of interest.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
